---
title: Truffle Umami Blast Burgers with Parmesan Frico, Potato Wedges & Crisp Green Salad
description: This bodacious burger is the definition of “umami.” It’s positively bursting with sumptuous, savory flavors sure to knock any burger aficionado's socks off. All-beef patties are flecked with truffle zest, then seared to juicy perfection. On top, there’s a pile of buttery sautéed mushrooms, a shatteringly-crisp Parmesan frico, and luscious truffle cream. It’s all tucked into brioche buns and served with crispy potato wedges and a fresh green salad with pickled shallots on the side. Yeah, these are the type of burgers you may feel compelled to break out the fine china for.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e0fb56c381eb932f756ea17-883cc3c6.jpg
